title: NYC Crime Report with Pat Dixon 2016-09-19
description: Tonightâ€™s NYCCR begins with news on the bombing over the weekend in Chelsea, Clayton Fletcher, Chelsea White, and Rich Carucci sit panel to talk about the bombing, Mayor de Blasio, the bombing suspect in custody, Helene Witt, Mandy Stadtmiller, and James Blond chime in, and Jacque von Strapp Skypes in. The crew then discusses the NY cleaver wielder and the cop that got slashed, Chis Laker reports from Penn Station, we hear from a few callers (one being Mia Vallis), they go on to talk about a Brooklyn stabbing, and Helene talks halal. We wrap up hearing about babysitting gone wrong, Chris Laker pops back in with a name chance and presidential predictions, Mandy talks about killing her dog, Pat talks about an untaken deal for a sex offender and Tinder gone wrong, Chris Laker gives his hot take on Tinder, and Shane Morrison sings us out with a song
